metadata.name: Dawn Mood
metadata.description:
A peaceful dawn, a calm sea washing around beach defences, a status quo between nature and humankind maintained.

Photographed at Bournemouth, in Dorset, southwest England.

As a huge thankyou, a beautiful acrylic print is available to the purchaser of this NFT, included within the price.

Copyright for the original image remains with Nigel Hicks. The purchaser of this NFT holds this jpeg, and has the right to view and to make a personal print. No commercial rights are conferred.
